    public class Game
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.MouseWheelListener
    The main controller class for Minecraft 2. Is a JFrame that holds a panel inside that runs the game. Game is a listens to the buttons on the main menu, the mouse, the mouse buttons, and the mouse wheel for events and acts accordingly.
    Author:
    Gary Fleming, Logun DeLeon, Alexander Duncanson
    See Also:
